Photo: Christopher MoagiThe MEC also reflected on Zodwa’s way of dressing, saying it was not acceptable.Zodwa said she was only trying to live her life.“I have realised that many people do not like what I do but this is how I like to live my life. “My aim is not to offend anyone but merely to entertain because I make a living out of it. “For example, I will be performing in Namibia soon and that is what I want to focus on. “I know I have been criticised all over but other people still appreciate me and respect what I do.”